<i>noun</i>: 핍박 [핍빡], 박해 [바캐] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>핍박 [핍빡]</dt><br>
<dd>persecution</dd><br>
<dd>강하게 억눌러서 몹시 괴롭게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of distressing someone terribly by oppressing him/her severely.</dd><br>
<dt>박해 [바캐]</dt><br>
<dd>persecution; oppression</dd><br>
<dd>힘이나 권력을 가지고 다른 사람을 괴롭히거나 못살게 굴어서 해롭게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of harassing or tormenting and causing harm to another person with one's power or authority.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>